<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Posts on 习七</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on 习七</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</managingEditor><webMaster>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 11:27:10 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://it-boyer.github.io/post/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>重新定义知识库：临场发挥，不要局限于经验，要善用AI大数据</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 11:25:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93/</guid><description>场景演练万事先，何苦人生无彩排书到用时方恨少，古来世人阅历深万卷速食碎片化，信息爆炸日日新经验难成无系统，人如浮萍薄纸命何以成长集大成，轻重</description></item><item><title>爆款视频的底层逻辑</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/%E7%9F%AD%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%95%E5%B1%82%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 12:58:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/%E7%9F%AD%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%95%E5%B1%82%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/</guid><description>从业 6 年来，我发现刚开始做短视频的人都会问一个问题，就是为什么那些制作看着特别普通的短视频能够成为爆款，而自己花了好几个小时，甚至是好几天用</description></item><item><title>怎么持续产出高质量的短视频?</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E4%BA%A7%E5%87%BA%E9%AB%98%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%AD%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Oct 2023 22:06:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E4%BA%A7%E5%87%BA%E9%AB%98%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%AD%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/</guid><description>现在短视频的创作门槛越来越低，似乎每个人只要拿起手机就可以拍出一段短视频。拍短视频一夜爆火的现象当然有，但这只是个例。想要持续产出高质量的短</description></item><item><title>拍短视频可以给我们带来什么?</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/%E6%8B%8D%E7%9F%AD%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%84/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Oct 2023 19:43:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/%E6%8B%8D%E7%9F%AD%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%84/</guid><description>一说起拍短视频的好处，我总是会想起我见证过的千千万万的小故事。故事的主角全部都是像你我一样的普通人，但是他们通过拍摄短视频，最终在人群中闪闪</description></item><item><title>老年迪斯科慢动作口令</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E8%BF%AA%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%91%E8%88%9E%E6%AD%A5/</link><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 10:20:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E8%BF%AA%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%91%E8%88%9E%E6%AD%A5/</guid><description>左脚前踩，再后踩，双手两边甩 左恰恰，右恰恰，左右左，右左右 前点三次，手交叉，321 收，321 收 左并步，右并步 迈步前点，后点前，迈步前点，后点</description></item><item><title>重新定义晨练：开篇诗以角色为主题，激活心灵演练设计愿景</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%99%A8%E7%BB%83/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Oct 2023 20:46:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%99%A8%E7%BB%83/</guid><description>晨练开篇定基调，专注角色设愿景 健康学习建社交，主角鲜明投精力 试炼七天迭代起，打怪升级通关制 均衡成长除恶习，效能达人造时势</description></item><item><title>截止时间</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Oct 2023 18:26:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/</guid><description>事无缓急志空谈，时不待人思易迁 以终为始布全局，要事第一行亦艰</description></item><item><title>水上舞台</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Oct 2023 18:25:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0/</guid><description>熙攘老友消食伴，怀旧 DJ 劲舞团 碧绿湖心夜更艳，半轮皓月金秋单</description></item><item><title>演练人生</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E6%BC%94%E7%BB%83%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Oct 2023 18:23:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E6%BC%94%E7%BB%83%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F/</guid><description>撰写剧本主人翁，构思推演江湖梦 吸星大法集大成，藏经阁外扫地僧</description></item><item><title>秋风凉</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E7%A7%8B%E9%A3%8E%E5%87%89/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Oct 2023 18:22:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E7%A7%8B%E9%A3%8E%E5%87%89/</guid><description>银杏树下人妖娆，金风玉露贴花黄 一叶知秋花见少，静待硕果满枝摇</description></item></channel></rss>